    recommended_approach:"SEB is a high-value target best approached through the wealth management angle. Approach: (1) Engage the Wealth/Private Banking CTO or Head of Digital, (2) Lead with Backbase Wealth — this is their crown jewel business, (3) Corporate RM tools (Assist) as a strong secondary angle, (4) SME banking as a growth story, (5) Leverage SEB's openness to vendor solutions — they're not as NIH as some Nordic peers, (6) Expected sales cycle: 12-18 months."
