    recommended_approach:"Handelsbanken is a compelling target because the need is acute and acknowledged. Approach: (1) UK transformation is the strongest entry point — position Backbase as the digital banking platform for the new UK model, (2) Employee Assist angle resonates with Handelsbanken's culture — enhancing the branch manager rather than replacing them, (3) Engage through UK CTO/COO for UK transformation or Group CTO for Nordic digital, (4) Be sensitive to the decentralized culture — avoid language about 'centralizing' or 'standardizing', use 'enabling' and 'empowering', (5) Expected sales cycle: 9-12 months for UK (urgency), 12-18 months for Nordic."
